LRS - Lowest cost option with basic protection against server rack and drive failures. Recommended for non-critical scenarios.
Geo-Redundant storage - Intermediate option with failover capabilities in a secondary region Recommended for backup scenarios.
Zone-redundant storage -Intermediate option with protection against data center-level failures. Recommended for high availability scenarios.
Geo-zone-redundant storage - Optimal data protection solution that includes the offerings of both GRS and ZRS. Recommended for critical data scenarios.

